window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Liberty lives.</b></p> <p>Despite the best efforts of their enemies, the city of Liberty still stands, and now Ryan Rosa and the rest of his guild are hell-bent on making sure they can withstand anything the guilds throw at them.</p> <p>But can they withstand the challenges the game has in store for them? Danger doesn't just come from other players...</p> <p><i>Empire of the Rose</i> contains the classic LITRPG elements of leveling, dungeons, terrifying killer bunnies, crafting, and community building.</p>"; 
